FBIS4-64912 "drweu090_i_94003" FBIS-WEU-94-090 Daily Report 9 May 1994 FRANCE Juppe Conditions EU Eastward Expansion on Reform Juppe Conditions EU Eastward Expansion on Reform BR0905142894 Paris LE FIGARO in French 9 May 94 p 8 BR0905142894 Paris LE FIGARO French BFN [Text] Yesterday, Foreign Minister Alain Juppe said that any further enlargement of the European Union should be subordinated to an institutional reform. "The current rules must be adapted to ensure the functioning of a community of 20 to 25 countries. We have to put our European house in order," Alain Juppe stated yesterday on France Culture [radio].
